options.text: You will be asked to verify token ownership with your wallet
Staked & Stirred Private Reception @ DAS London
this is an exclusive gathering for top founders, investors, and operators shaping the future of web3.

Enjoy a refined evening of cocktails, conversation, and connection in an intimate setting. This private event is by invitation only, offering a premium space to unwind, connect, and get ahead of the signal.
RSVP early to confirm your spot

Blockdaemon is the institutional gateway to Web3, securing over $110B in digital assets for 400+ institutions, including exchanges, custodians, crypto platforms, and financial enterprises. We offer institutional-grade blockchain infrastructure spanning nodes, APIs, staking, MPC wallets and vaults. Since 2017, our globally distributed infrastructure ensures unrivaled security, compliance, and scalability. For more information visit:
Please register to see the exact location of this event.
